PREAMBLE

This License governs the use of a customer-facing e-commerce storefront
application (hereinafter "Storefront Software" or "Software"). The Storefront
Software includes but is not limited to: frontend user interfaces, customer
checkout flows, product catalogs, shopping cart implementations, and all
customer-interactive elements.

The Licensor retains all intellectual property rights in the Software and
imposes mandatory attribution requirements to ensure proper credit for the
original engineering work. These conditions are binding and non-waivable.

