BREACH DETECTION & ESCALATION

The Licensor may:

  1. AUTOMATED DETECTION: Monitor for violations through:
     • Crawling publicly deployed applications
     • Automated screenshot analysis
     • CSS inspection of deployed sites
     • GitHub repository scanning

  2. NOTIFICATION: Upon detection of any violation:
     • Issue a formal breach notice via email/GitHub
     • Specify exact violations and remediation steps
     • Provide 3 business days to respond

  3. CURE PERIOD:
     • First-time violations: 7 calendar days to cure
     • Subsequent violations by same licensee: 3 calendar days
     • Third+ violation: NO cure period, immediate termination

