TERMINATION AND ENFORCEMENT

1. AUTOMATIC TERMINATION
   Any violation of Conditions 1, 2, 3, or 4 immediately and automatically
   terminates all rights granted under this License without notice. Upon
   termination you must:
     • Immediately cease all use and deployment
     • Remove the Storefront Software from all live environments within 24 hours
     • Notify the Licensor of compliance
     • Destroy all local copies

2. CURE PERIOD AND REINSTATEMENT
   Violations detected before deployment: 14 days to cure, unlimited reinstatements
   Violations in deployed applications: 7 days for first violation
   Repeated violations: 3 days, then permanent termination with no further reinstatement

3. DAMAGES & ENFORCEMENT
   Violations constitute copyright infringement and breach of contract.
   As damages are difficult to calculate, you agree to pay upon demand:
     • $500 USD per day of violation (calculated from detection date)
     • $10,000 USD per instance of header removal
     • $25,000 USD per hidden/obscured credit block
     • Legal fees and court costs (if litigation required)
     • Injunctive relief forcing immediate removal from deployment

4. GOVERNING LAW AND JURISDICTION
   This License is governed by the laws of India and subject to exclusive
   jurisdiction of Indian courts. If you are outside India, you:
     • Consent to Indian court jurisdiction
     • Waive any objections to forum non conveniens
     • Agree to bear costs of international enforcement

